data.description: Yes, it is true, this property has so much to offer. 40 acres more or less just minutes to I65! Private, convenient and endless possibilities.  Property has a pond, open grazing area, fenced areas and woods. Plenty of wildlife reside on the property as well. Large barn, fenced areas that would be perfect for horses. The brick home has so much to offer and can be updated to fit any lifestyle. 3,000 sg ft. of heated and cooling space, there is room for everyone. Primary bedroom is oversized, large laundry room with storage space, formal dining area and den, 3 additional bedrooms on the main floor, oversized family room in basement. The garage has space for a hobby area. If you have been looking for land and a home to create your own style, this is it!!!
